1
00:00:19,020 --> 00:00:21,910
[Blind Woman]

2
00:00:23,070 --> 00:00:25,910
[Episode 19: Sorry, I Lied to You]

3
00:00:35,070 --> 00:00:35,630
What's wrong?

4
00:00:38,610 --> 00:00:41,180
Recently, there have been a lot of troubles at home,

5
00:00:41,770 --> 00:00:43,000
so I brought a gun for self-defense.

6
00:00:44,170 --> 00:00:45,360
Did I scare you?

7
00:00:47,670 --> 00:00:48,350
Of course not.

8
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:49,920
That's good.

9
00:00:50,900 --> 00:00:51,410
Go.

10
00:00:52,290 --> 00:00:53,180
Thank you, Master Yu.

11
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:09,990
Who are you?

12
00:01:12,789 --> 00:01:13,270
It's me.

13
00:01:16,590 --> 00:01:17,780
Miss asked me to save you.

14
00:01:19,870 --> 00:01:20,630
Wanyue?

15
00:01:22,530 --> 00:01:23,780
What is your relationship with Wanyue?

16
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:25,280
Why do you have so many questions?

17
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:26,730
Where is she?

18
00:01:27,170 --> 00:01:28,710
She's at Yu's Mansion, packing her things.

19
00:01:29,020 --> 00:01:29,940
She's moving out?

20
00:01:35,750 --> 00:01:37,160
Get changed and come with me.

21
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:05,840
Something is wrong!

22
00:02:06,060 --> 00:02:06,940
Stop them!

23
00:02:10,460 --> 00:02:11,680
Miss, go!

24
00:02:11,700 --> 00:02:12,260
Wu You!

25
00:02:13,310 --> 00:02:13,750
No!

26
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:14,920
-Wu You!
-Let's go!

27
00:02:15,300 --> 00:02:16,180
-Let's go.
-No!

28
00:02:16,470 --> 00:02:17,150
-Wu You!
-Let's go!

29
00:02:17,430 --> 00:02:18,110
Wu You!

30
00:02:29,130 --> 00:02:30,280
Director Wu.

31
00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:37,070
Weren't you very arrogant before?

32
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:41,480
But now you're in my hands.

33
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:47,030
Yu Zhenhai, you scumbag.

34
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,470
Wu You,

35
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,800
tell me,

36
00:02:53,940 --> 00:02:58,810
what exactly is your relationship with Lin Wanyue?

37
00:02:59,440 --> 00:03:00,750
A scumbag like you

38
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,110
doesn't deserve to know.

39
00:03:11,350 --> 00:03:12,160
Will you speak or not?

40
00:03:13,370 --> 00:03:14,130
Will you speak or not?

41
00:03:14,690 --> 00:03:15,200
I will!

42
00:03:15,910 --> 00:03:16,590
I'll tell you.

43
00:03:17,020 --> 00:03:17,810
-Tell me.
-I'll tell you.

44
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,560
Yu Zhenhai,

45
00:03:20,140 --> 00:03:22,310
your death is near.

46
00:03:32,110 --> 00:03:33,670
Lock him up.

47
00:03:34,500 --> 00:03:37,370
I'm going to set a trap!

48
00:03:37,860 --> 00:03:38,680
Yes, Chairman.

49
00:03:39,430 --> 00:03:39,940
Go!

50
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,010
Wanyue,

51
00:03:48,230 --> 00:03:49,630
What's your relationship with Wu You?

52
00:03:50,140 --> 00:03:51,210
Why did he come to save me?

53
00:03:53,030 --> 00:03:53,630
Yanchuan.

54
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,190
Actually, my name is not Lin Wanyue.

55
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,120
My name is Jiang Chan.

56
00:04:01,130 --> 00:04:02,180
Jiang Chan?

57
00:04:04,910 --> 00:04:06,430
You really are Uncle Jiang's daughter?

58
00:04:06,930 --> 00:04:09,050
I was supposed to die in that big fire.

59
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,290
It was your mother who saved me,

60
00:04:11,310 --> 00:04:12,310
allowing me to escape that disaster.

61
00:04:12,910 --> 00:04:14,380
Later, I was sent to an welfare house.

62
00:04:15,110 --> 00:04:16,430
And I met Wu You there.

63
00:04:18,750 --> 00:04:20,230
So you and Wu You have known each other for a long time.

64
00:04:21,410 --> 00:04:22,440
Why didn't you tell me?

65
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:27,520
I'm sorry.

66
00:04:29,830 --> 00:04:31,430
Because the one who killed our families

67
00:04:32,420 --> 00:04:34,450
and set the warehouse on fire

68
00:04:35,950 --> 00:04:37,460
was your father, Yu Zhenhai.

69
00:04:40,270 --> 00:04:41,200
My father?

70
00:04:42,659 --> 00:04:43,460
Back then, your father

71
00:04:44,159 --> 00:04:45,360
was selling opium with Wu Yingtian,

72
00:04:45,409 --> 00:04:46,970
Lai Guangsheng, Zhong Cheng,

73
00:04:47,090 --> 00:04:47,930
and his wife.

74
00:04:49,130 --> 00:04:50,420
At that time, the entire Jiangcheng

75
00:04:50,970 --> 00:04:52,680
was in chaos, and the people were suffering.

76
00:04:53,490 --> 00:04:55,240
My father discovered their crimes.

77
00:04:55,850 --> 00:04:57,730
When they failed to lure him to their side, they killed him to silence him.

78
00:04:59,290 --> 00:05:00,440
To destroy the evidence,

79
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,880
they set fire to the entire Yunhai warehouse and burned it down.

80
00:05:06,550 --> 00:05:07,400
My parents,

81
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:09,720
Xiang's sister,

82
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,480
and Wu You's mother

83
00:05:12,430 --> 00:05:14,110
died in that fire.

84
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,230
And everyone

85
00:05:17,730 --> 00:05:18,610
in the warehouse

86
00:05:19,540 --> 00:05:21,150
died.

87
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,940
[File]

88
00:05:25,380 --> 00:05:27,330
This is the evidence of all the crimes committed by your father.

89
00:06:03,010 --> 00:06:05,010
So, from the moment we first met

90
00:06:07,210 --> 00:06:09,450
to everything that happened later in the Yu family,

91
00:06:10,970 --> 00:06:12,820
even Wu Yingtian's death,

92
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:16,310
was all planned by you, Wu You,

93
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:19,270
and the victims

94
00:06:19,980 --> 00:06:21,010
of that fire?

95
00:06:21,740 --> 00:06:22,330
Yes.

96
00:06:23,770 --> 00:06:24,940
Everything was done by us.

97
00:06:25,970 --> 00:06:26,880
It was for revenge,

98
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:30,250
for those who died in the fire.

99
00:06:35,670 --> 00:06:36,480
Miss Jiang,

100
00:06:39,220 --> 00:06:40,820
thank you for rescuing me from Yu's Mansion.

101
00:06:47,090 --> 00:06:47,730
Wanyue,

102
00:06:52,010 --> 00:06:53,060
tell me.

103
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:57,400
Besides revenge,

104
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:00,480
have you...

105
00:07:02,670 --> 00:07:04,670
have you ever truly loved me?

106
00:07:10,290 --> 00:07:13,350
♫As I cross that sky♫

107
00:07:13,370 --> 00:07:16,130
♫Who will be waiting for me?♫

108
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:21,960
♫Dreams are like clouds that will bloom♫

109
00:07:22,330 --> 00:07:23,210
I see.

110
00:07:22,540 --> 00:07:25,320
♫Every time the sunlight spills through the window♫

111
00:07:25,350 --> 00:07:28,010
♫It's like your little dimples♫

112
00:07:28,580 --> 00:07:31,820
♫In the depths of time♫

113
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:34,590
♫It gently shines on me♫

114
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:34,560
Yu Yanchuan,

115
00:07:34,620 --> 00:07:37,600
♫You said that by turning over those lonely pages♫

116
00:07:35,340 --> 00:07:36,070
I'm sorry.

117
00:07:36,870 --> 00:07:38,720
We're destined not to get together.

118
00:07:37,659 --> 00:07:40,380
♫I would see the flowers♫

119
00:07:39,490 --> 00:07:40,850
But I'll keep my love for you

120
00:07:40,830 --> 00:07:46,330
♫In colors of sky blue and pink♫

121
00:07:42,220 --> 00:07:43,370
a secret.

122
00:07:44,390 --> 00:07:45,270
Wanyue,

123
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:48,460
♫I'm glad I walked with you♫

124
00:07:46,890 --> 00:07:48,810
what's more painful than loving someone but not being loved in return

125
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:52,150
♫And arrived in this different space and time♫

126
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,750
is not even having the right to love her.

127
00:07:52,610 --> 00:07:55,860
♫The future has fallen into my eyes♫

128
00:07:55,890 --> 00:07:58,840
♫I lift my head high♫

129
00:08:00,260 --> 00:08:05,860
♫I'm glad I arrived in this different space and time♫

130
00:08:06,230 --> 00:08:08,570
[Prosperity Rising]

131
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:09,080
♫To meet a better version of me♫

132
00:08:09,670 --> 00:08:10,600
Brothers and sisters,

133
00:08:11,590 --> 00:08:13,040
this time, our plan is to split into two teams

134
00:08:13,070 --> 00:08:13,870
to rescue Wu You.

135
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:17,050
One team will go with Hu to set up an ambush at the Donglin warehouse,

136
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:19,640
while the other will go with me to Yu's Mansion

137
00:08:19,890 --> 00:08:21,450
to lure Yu Zhenhai and rescue Wu You.

138
00:08:22,250 --> 00:08:23,280
Do you understand?

139
00:08:23,930 --> 00:08:24,650
Yes!

140
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:25,730
Okay.

141
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,480
Let's go now.

142
00:08:28,550 --> 00:08:29,080
Let's go.

143
00:08:31,630 --> 00:08:32,320
Wu You,

144
00:08:33,150 --> 00:08:33,840
I will definitely rescue you

145
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,440
from Yu Zhenhai's hands.

146
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:46,950
Miss.

147
00:08:54,190 --> 00:08:57,830
Miss Lin, you are really bold.

148
00:08:59,060 --> 00:09:00,940
You actually brought only one person with you.

149
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:01,830
Master Yu,

150
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:04,650
I'm not here to fight with you.

151
00:09:05,370 --> 00:09:08,050
I'm here to make a deal with you.

152
00:09:08,890 --> 00:09:09,720
A deal?

153
00:09:10,630 --> 00:09:11,710
What kind of deal

154
00:09:12,010 --> 00:09:13,800
could there be between us?

155
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:15,910
Do you remember the batch of opium

156
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:18,310
that Zhong Cheng lost?

157
00:09:27,270 --> 00:09:29,200
That is in your hands?

158
00:09:30,580 --> 00:09:31,150
Yes.

159
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,120
How can you prove it?

160
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:37,880
[Yu's Business Association]

161
00:09:45,580 --> 00:09:46,650
Do you believe me now?

162
00:09:48,790 --> 00:09:49,390
Alright.

163
00:09:50,190 --> 00:09:51,160
What do you want me to do?

164
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:53,650
Let Wu You go,

165
00:09:54,490 --> 00:09:55,330
and I'll give you the goods.

166
00:09:57,550 --> 00:09:58,360
Wu You?

167
00:10:00,950 --> 00:10:04,160
What's your relationship with Wu You?

168
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:07,080
Why does he deserve you doing this for him?

169
00:10:07,870 --> 00:10:08,670
He saved me.

170
00:10:09,910 --> 00:10:10,910
I'm returning the favor to him.

171
00:10:11,340 --> 00:10:12,910
What if I don't let him go?

172
00:10:14,550 --> 00:10:16,980
Then I'll give the opium to the police.

173
00:10:24,470 --> 00:10:25,040
Alright.

174
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:26,790
Deal.

175
00:10:28,100 --> 00:10:28,910
Release Wu You.

176
00:10:29,090 --> 00:10:29,730
Yes, Master.

177
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:40,990
Miss,

178
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:42,910
be careful.

179
00:10:43,810 --> 00:10:44,740
Take him to the hospital.

180
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:45,480
Yes.

181
00:10:48,170 --> 00:10:48,930
Lin Wanyue,

182
00:10:49,670 --> 00:10:51,550
if you lie to me,

183
00:10:52,410 --> 00:10:53,800
I won't let you go.

184
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:55,550
May our cooperation be pleasant.

185
00:11:11,810 --> 00:11:14,290
It seems that I will easily get something

186
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:16,240
I've been tirelessly searching for.

187
00:11:16,690 --> 00:11:17,420
Open it.

188
00:11:17,790 --> 00:11:18,240
Yes.

189
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:31,370
Master, this opium is fake.

190
00:11:32,570 --> 00:11:33,180
Impossible.

191
00:11:33,590 --> 00:11:35,800
Lin Wanyue, how dare you lie to me?

192
00:11:35,850 --> 00:11:36,490
I didn't.

193
00:11:36,770 --> 00:11:37,680
I don't know anything!

194
00:11:38,110 --> 00:11:38,680
Kill her!
